94
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,160
State Counselor,

95
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,040
following your orders,

96
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,720
I've given the Seventh Prince
the Qianji poison.

97
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,430
Well done.

98
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,800
Your Majesty.

99
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,920
This is a family lunch.
No need for etiquette.

100
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,270
Just sit with Si.

101
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,800
Thank you, Your Majesty.

